•	Winand R, et al. Investigating fungal diversity through metabarcoding for environmental samples: assessment of ITS1 and ITS2 Illumina sequencing using multiple defined mock communities with different classification methods and reference databases. DOI: 10.1186/s12864-025-11917-y
•	Polanco FA, et al. A Confidence Scoring Procedure for eDNA Metabarcoding Records and Its Application to a Global Marine Fish Dataset. DOI: 10.1002/edn3.70077
